{"tid":2062154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應拜登指敗選或賴賬 川普首談敗選動向","createTime":"2020-06-13T02:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T05:08:06.000Z","uid":28765,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1eac979da9cd62383633438568248f50bc8c3cf7","tid":2062154,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T02:51:49.000Z","msg":"2020-06-13 10:23:37<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n現任總統川普因武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情及佛洛伊德之死，選情不被外界看好，代表民主黨參選的前副總統拜登甚至擔憂，川普敗選恐會「賴帳」。對此，川普回應說，「輸了就是輸了，我會去做其它事情。」<br />\n<br />\n川普當地時間週五接受《福斯新聞》專訪時，被問到如何看待拜登的「賴帳說」，川普表示，「如果我輸了，那我就是輸了，我的意思是，我會去做其它事情。」但川普也強調，自己若敗選，對美國來說會是非常糟糕的一件事。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3196472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3196472&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=71c2b606\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3196472&h=0103326d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3196472</a>"},{"pid":"06da74431efd4df8b2e9816e9038c12826b0d243","tid":2062154,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T02:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e83999afb40b621eaf869b2340dcca7c3c4766b","tid":2062154,"uid":131767,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T02:57:24.000Z","msg":"答咗記者一個問題就變咗做首談敗選<br />\n好似講到就輸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ad462d696738263224504b6252b337c8cb69be","tid":2062154,"uid":42340,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T03:01:56.000Z","msg":"侵今次咁都贏到<br />\n我切丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif